<BR><FONT POINT-SIZE="8"><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">Diebold, Incorporated
is a global leader in card-based transaction systems, security and service
solutions.</FONT>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT>&nbsp;

<P><FONT POINT-SIZE="8"><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">We develop, manufacture,
sell and service automated teller machines (ATMs), campus systems, smart
card systems, electronic and physical security equipment, automated medication
dispensing systems, software and integrated systems solutions.</FONT>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT>&nbsp;

<P><FONT POINT-SIZE="8"><FONT FACE="Arial,Helvetica">Headquartered in Canton,
Ohio, Diebold has international offices in Canada, Mexico, the United Kingdom,
Germany, Singapore, Venezuela, India and China; and manufacturing operations
in the United States, Germany, China and India.</FONT>&nbsp;</FONT></TD>

